'''[[shop]] [[time]]''' (''uncountable'')

# (Automotive and heavy equipment) When a [[vehicle]] or [[machine]] is out of [[service]] for [[repair]], the time out of service is called ''shop time''.
# (Foundry and machine shop) When a [[foundry]] or [[machine shop]] produces a custom item, the time spent making it may be billed as ''shop time''.